Tile: Sign up system
Description:
Customers will sign up for an account with their Name,
Address, Phone Number and email
 
Title: Customer interactions
They will be able to browse the chefs recipes aswell as chat in a chat room with other 
members of the website.

Title: online payment for food
Description: 
The customers can attach a credit card to their account and prepay for meals online. 
They can authorize payment before they come. You can also authorize payment and tip the waiters 
by the click of a button.
 
Title: reservations
Description:
The customers can make reservations online before they come. They must make the reservation 1 week ahead of time